3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Kharge%20has%20suggested%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi%20that%20the%20siblings%20not%20contesting%20from%20the%20two%20seats%20--%20their%20family%20bastions%20for%20decades%20--%20would%20send%20a%20wrong%20message%2C%20not%20just%20to%20party%20workers%20but%20to%20the%20Opposition%2C%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20and%20the%20voters%20as%20well.%20The%20ramifications%20will%20be%20felt%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20had%20handed%20Mr%20Kharge%20the%20responsibility%20of%20choosing%20a%20candidate%2C%20after%20which%20he%20had%20a%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Gandhi%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20an%20attempt%20to%20win%20back%20Amethi%2C%20which%20he%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Union%20minster%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%202019%2C%20after%20representing%20it%20in%20parliament%20for%20three%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20though%2C%20remains%20firm%20on%20her%20decision%20not%20to%20contest%20despite%20much%20pressure.%20There%20was%20widespread%20expectation%20that%20she%20would%20step%20into%20her%20mother's%20shoes%20in%20Raebareli.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20representing%20Raebareli%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20since%202004%20but%20this%20year%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20delaying%20the%20decision%20on%20candidates%20for%20the%20two%20seats%20for%20weeks.%20But%20now%2C%20the%20time%20has%20almost%20run%20out.%20Two%20days%20ago%2C%20Congress%20workers%20went%20into%20protest%20mode%20in%20Amethi%2C%20seeking%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20as%20candidate.%20Election%20for%20both%20seats%20is%20due%20on%20May%2020%2C%20the%20fifth%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20reports%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20may%20not%20be%20interested%20in%20contesting%20from%20Amethi.%20A%20victory%20would%20mean%20that%20he%20might%20have%20to%20surrender%20the%20Kerala%20seat%2C%20which%20sent%20him%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20sources%20hinted%20that%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20reluctance%20stems%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20her%20victory%20from%20Raebareli%20would%20place%20all%20three%20Gandhi%20family%20members%20in%20parliament%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20BJP%20accusation%20of%20dynasty%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20of%20353%20seats%20are%20due%20in%20the%20remaining%20five%20phases.%20Of%20these%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20contesting%20on%20330%20seats.%20This%20is%20the%20lowest%20number%20of%20seats%20the%20Congress%20has%20contested%20in%20since%20Independence.%20The%20reason%20is%20the%20united%20front%20the%20Opposition%20is%20putting%20up%20and%20many%20of%20the%20seats%20have%20been%20conceded%20to%20allies%20in%20various%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714659720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fva0951pg_rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-mallikarjun-kharge-rahul-gandhi-meet-to-discuss-amethi-raebareli-5572293%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20suspense%20over%20Congress%20candidates%20in%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20has%20been%20dialled%20up%20a%20notch%2C%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20being%20given%20a%20few%20more%20hours%20to%20make%20their%20decision.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-mallikarjun-kharge-rahul-gandhi-meet-to-discuss-amethi-raebareli-5572293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-mallikarjun-kharge-rahul-gandhi-meet-to-discuss-amethi-raebareli-5572293%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news