ed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2024-05-01%2Fla-me-ucla-camp-police%5C%22%3ELos%20Angeles%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officers%20muscled%20their%20way%20into%20the%20campus%20in%20the%20pre-dawn%20hours%20around%203.15%20am%20PDT%20(3.45%20pm%20IST)%20to%20arrest%20occupants%20who%20refused%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUCLA%20BREAKING%20%F0%9F%9A%A8%20%3A%20CHP%20RIOT%20POLICE%20HAVE%20BROKEN%20THROUGH%2C%20POLICE%20HAVE%20BREACHED%20THE%20ENCAMPMENT.%20PEOPLE%20BEING%20DETAINED.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FuxcAOReRp5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FuxcAOReRp5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Anthony%20Cabassa%20(%40AnthonyCabassa_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnthonyCabassa_%2Fstatus%2F1785987471446262228%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20started%20around%20sunset%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20around%20300%20to%20500%20police%20officers%20were%20seen%20inside%20the%20camp%20while%20around%202%2C000%20more%20gathered%20outside%20the%20barriacades%20when%20the%20officers%20in%20tactical%20gear%20first%20began%20filing%20onto%20the%20UCLA%20campus%2C%20Reuters%20reported%20quoting%20a%20local%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20used%20flash-bang%20tupe%20devices%20that%20echoed%20across%20the%20campus%2C%20as%20per%20reports.%20Some%20protesters%20fought%20back%20while%20shouting%2C%20%26quot%3Bpush%20them%20back%26quot%3B%20and%20flashing%20bright%20lights%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20police.Some%20of%20them%20had%20been%20seen%20donning%20hard%20hats%2C%20goggles%20and%20respirator%20masks%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20siege%20a%20day%20after%20the%20university%20declared%20the%20encampment%20unlawful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20repeated%20loudspeaker%20announcements%2C%20police%20asked%20demonstrators%20to%20clear%20the%20protest%20zone%20before%20moving%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20CLASH%20BEFORE%20THE%20CRACKDOWN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20masked%20counter-demonstrators%20launched%20a%20surprise%20assault%20on%20the%20tent%20city%20leading%20to%20a%20violenct%20clash%20between%20the%20encampment's%20occupants.%20The%20occupants%20of%20the%20outdoor%20protest%20camp%2C%20set%20up%20last%20week%2C%20had%20remained%20otherwise%20peaceful%20before%20the%20clash%2C%20in%20which%20both%20sides%20traded%20blows%20and%20doused%20each%20other%20with%20pepper%20spray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20confrontation%20went%20on%20for%20two%20or%20three%20hours%20into%20early%20Wednesday%20morning%20before%20police%20restored%20order.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20California%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20later%20criticized%20the%20%26quot%3Blimited%20and%20delayed%20campus%20law%20enforcement%20response%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20unrest%20as%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20clashes%2C%20the%20university%20said%20the%20campus%2C%20which%20enrolls%20nearly%2052%2C000%20students%2C%20including%20undergraduates%20and%20graduate%20scholars%2C%20would%20remain%20shuttered%20except%20for%20limited%20operations%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColumbia%20University%20Protests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20action%20in%20UCLA%20came%20a%20day%20after%20police%20in%20New%20York%20City%20arrested%20pro-Palestinian%20activists%20who%20occupied%20a%20building%20at%20Columbia%20University%20and%20removed%20a%20tent%20city%20from%20the%20campus%20of%20the%20Ivy%20League%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%20at%20UCLA%20and%20in%20New%20York%20were%20part%20of%20the%20biggest%20outpouring%20of%20US%20student%20activism%20since%20the%20anti-racism%20rallies%20and%20marches%20of%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20have%20rallied%20or%20set%20up%20tent%20en