20the%20parcel%20and%20how%20it%20exploded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Mahendra%20Prasad)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714646340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fuhes788_gujarat-blast_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-daughter-die-as-parcel-explodes-at-gujarat-home-cops-launch-probe-5572093%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20parcel%20exploded%20after%20being%20delivered%20to%20the%20house%20of%20a%20man%20in%20Gujarat%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-daughter-die-as-parcel-explodes-at-gujarat-home-cops-launch-probe-5572093%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-daughter-die-as-parcel-explodes-at-gujarat-home-cops-launch-probe-5572093%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-daughter-die-as-parcel-explodes-at-gujarat-home-cops-launch-probe-5572093%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kim%20Jong%20Un%20Picks%2025%20''Pretty''%20Girls%20For%20His%20''Pleasure%20Squad''%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYeonmi%20Park%2C%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20escaped%C2%A0from%C2%A0North%20Korea%2C%20has%20revealed%20sensational%20things%20about%20the%20country's%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fweird-news%2Fkim-jong-un-picks-25-32703053%5C%22%3EMirror%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20Ms%20Park%20claimed%20that%20Kim%20Jong-un%20picks%2025%20virgin%20girls%20every%20year%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bpleasure%20squad%26quot%3B.%20Notably%2C%20the%20women%20are%20picked%20based%20on%20their%20looks%20and%20political%20loyalty.%20She%20further%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20scouted%20twice%20for%20Kim's%20''pleasure%20squad''%20but%C2%A0was%20not%20selected%C2%A0due%20to%20her%20family%20status.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defector%20said%3A%20''They%20visit%20every%20classroom%20and%20they%20even%20go%20to%20schoolyards%20in%20case%20they%20missed%20someone%20pretty.%20Once%20they%20find%20some%20pretty%20girls%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20they%20do%20is%20check%20into%20their%20family%20status%20and%20their%20political%20status.%20They%20eliminate%20any%20girls%20with%20family%20members%20that%20have%20escaped%20from%20North%20Korea%2C%20or%20have%20relatives%20in%20South%20Korea%20or%20other%20countries.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claims%20that%20once%20the%20girls%20are%20selected%2C%C2%A0they%20are%20made%20to%20undergo%20medical%20examinations%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20virgins.%20During%20the%20test%2C%20%26quot%3Beven%20the%20smallest%20defect%26quot%3B%20like%20a%20minor%20scar%2C%20leads%20to%20disqualification.%C2%A0After%20rigorous%20testing%2C%20only%20a%20few%20girls%20from%20across%20North%20Korea%20are%20then%20sent%20to%20Pyongyang%20where%20their%20sole%20purpose%20is%20to%20gratify%20the%20dictator's%20desires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20squad%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20distinct%20groups%2C%20with%20one%20trained%20in%20massage%2C%20and%20the%20other%20in%20performing%20songs%20and%20dances.%20The%20third%20group%20has%20to%20be%20sexually%20intimate%20with%20the%20dictator%20and%20other%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20to%20be%20sexually%20intimate%20with%20the%20dictator%2C%20and%20other%20men.%20They%20have%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20please%20these%20men%20that's%20their%20only%20goal%2C''%20Ms%20Park%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20most%20attractive%20girls%20are%20selected%20to%20serve%20the%20dictator%20himself%2C%20others%20are%20assigned%20to%20satisfy%20lower-ranking%20generals%20and%20politicians.%C2%A0The%20report%20further%20stated%20that%20once%20the%20members%20of%20the%20squad%20reach%20their%20mid-twenties%2C%20their%20tenure%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20often%20married%20to%20the%20leader's%20bodyguards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Park%20explained%20that%20the%20origins%20of%20this%20%26quot%3Bpleasure%20squad%26quot%3B%20date%20back%20to%20the%201970s%20era%20of%20Kim%20Jong-un's%20father%2C%20Kim%20Jong-II%20who%20believed%20that%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20sexual%20intimacy%20would%20give%20him%20immortality.''%C2%A0However%2C%20he%20died%20in%202011%20from%20a%20massive%20heart%20attack%2C%20aged%2070.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714646280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fkim-jong-un-reuters_650x400_61521176034.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-un-handpicks-25-pretty-girls-every-year-for-his-pleasure-squad-report-5571989%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20claims%20that%20once%20the%20girls%20are%20selected%2C%20they%20are%20made%20to%20undergo%20medical%20examinations%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20virgins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-un-handpicks-25-pretty-girls-every-year-for-his-pleasure-squad-report-5571989%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-un-handpicks-25-pretty-girls-every-year-for-his-pleasure-squad-report-5571989%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-un-handpicks-25-pretty-girls-every-year-for-his-pleasure-squad-report-5571989%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cambodia%20blames%20heatwave%20for%20deadly%20ammo%20blast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714645830000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2cd7%2Flive%2F378d8fe0-0868-11ef-996e-29ade0d99634.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcrgy20