The%20restructuring%20strengthens%20Xi's%20direct%20oversight%20of%20the%20PLA's%20strategic%20capacities%20and%20emphasises%20China's%20aspirations%20to%20proficiently%20harness%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20and%20other%20emerging%20technologies%20in%20anticipation%20of%20what%20it%20terms%20the%20%26quot%3Bintelligentised%20warfare%26quot%3B%20of%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-unveils-new-cyber-force-to-fight-and-win-wars-5478716%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0China%20Unvei%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-unveils-new-cyber-force-to-fight-and-win-wars-5478716%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Els%20New%20Cyber%20Force%20To%20%26quot%3BFight%20And%20Win%26quot%3B%20Wars%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20critical%20for%20China%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20push%20its%20military%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20changing%20strategic%20realities%20and%20the%20rapidly%20evolving%20nature%20of%20contemporary%20warfare.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Beijing%20has%20pursued%20a%20comprehensive%20modernisation%20of%20its%20military%20capabilities%2C%20aiming%20to%20transform%20the%20PLA%20into%20a%20formidable%20force%20capable%20of%20safeguarding%20its%20interests%20regionally%20and%20globally.%20This%20modernisation%20drive%20has%20encompassed%20various%20aspects%2C%20including%20technological%20advancement%2C%20organisational%20reform%2C%20and%20doctrinal%20evolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreparing%20For%20Modern%20Warfare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20focal%20points%20of%20China's%20military%20modernisation%20has%20been%20the%20development%20and%20acquisition%20of%20advanced%20weaponry%20and%20equipment.%20This%20includes%20the%20enhancement%20of%20its%20naval%20capabilities%20with%20the%20commissioning%20of%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20modernisation%20of%20its%20air%20force%20with%20next-generation%20fighter%20jets%2C%20and%20bolstering%20its%20missile%20forces%20with%20advanced%20ballistic%20and%20cruise%20missiles.%20Additionally%2C%20China%20has%20invested%20heavily%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-plans-to-double-size-of-its-space-station-to-rival-nasa-4452260%5C%22%3Ecyber%20and%20space%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recognising%20their%20importance%20in%20modern%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20organisational%20reforms%20have%20been%20instituted%20to%20streamline%20command%20structures%2C%20improve%20joint%20operations%2C%20and%20enhance%20the%20overall%20efficiency%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20PLA.%20These%20reforms%20have%20included%20the%20establishment%20of%20new%20commands%20and%20theatre%20commands%2C%20as%20well%20as%20efforts%20to%20professionalise%20and%20modernise%20the%20military%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-head-bill-nelson-says-china-hiding-military-presence-in-space-5466869%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0China%20Hiding%20Military%20Presence%20In%20Space%3A%20NASA%20Head%20Bill%20Nelson%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20China's%20military%20modernisation%20poses%20several%20significant%20consequences%20for%20India%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20security%20dynamics%20and%20strategic%20calculations.%20Its%20enhanced%20military%20capabilities%2C%20particularly%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20naval%20expansion%2C%20missile%20development%2C%20and%20cyber%20warfare%2C%20could%20potentially%20tilt%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20the%20region%2C%20thereby%20altering%20the%20strategic%20landscape%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20India.%20The%20military%20modernisation%20seems%20to%20have%20already%20emboldened%20Beijing%20to%20assert%20its%20territorial%20claims%20more%20strongly%2C%20potentially%20heightening%20the%20risk%20of%20border%20skirmishes%20and%20military%20confrontations%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20This%20has%20exacerbated%20existing%20tensions%20and%20destabilised%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20India%20Should%20Pay%20Attention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20China's%20growing%20military%20prowess%20has%20implications%20for%20India's%20defence%20planning%20and%20security%20posture.%20New%20Delhi%20is%20compelled%20to%20invest%20more%20resources%20in%20its%20own%20military%20modernisation%20efforts%20to%20maintain%20a%20credible%20deterrent%20against%20potential%20Chinese%20aggression%2C%20which%20may%20require%20diverting%20resources%20away%20from%20other%20development%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20India%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20series%20of%20defence%20reforms%20aimed%20at%20modernising%20and%20enhancing%20the%20efficiency%20of%20its%20armed%20forces.%20One%20significant%20reform%20has%20been%20the%20promotion%20of%20indigenous%20defence%20manufacturing%20through%20initiatives%20like%20the%20%26quot%3BMake%20in%20India%26quot%3B%20programme.%20This%20initiative%20seeks%20to%20encourage%20domestic%20production%20of%20defence%20equipment%2C%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20imports%20and%20bolstering%20India's%20self-reliance%20in%20defence%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Make%20In%20India'%20Initiative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20focus%20on%20streamlining%20defence%20procurement%20processes%20to%20expedite%20the%20acquisition%20of%20critical%20military%20hardware%20and%20technology.%20Measures%20such%20as%20the%20Defense%20Acquisition%20Procedure%20(DAP)%20and%20the%20Strategic%20Partnership%20Model%20aim%20to%20facilitate%20smoother%20procurement%20processes%20and%20encourage%20private%20sector%20participation%20in%20defence%20production.%20There%20have%20also%20been%20efforts%20to%20enhance%20defence%20infrastructure%20along%20India's%20borders%2C%20particularly%20in%20border%20areas%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20the%20development%20of%20roads%2C%20airfields%2C%20and%20other%20infrastructure%20to%20improve%20mobility%20and%20logistical%20support%20for%20the%20armed%20forces.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20has%20been%20an%20emphasis%20on%20promoting%20jointness%20and%20integration%20among%20the%20three%20branches%20of%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20-%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20Navy%2C%20and%20the%20Air%20Force%20-%20to%20enhance%20operational%20synergy%20and%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20quicker%20reforms%20and%20broader%20restructuring.%20Indian%20debate%20on%20theatre%20commands%20is%20still%20in%20limbo%2C%20and%20rationalisation%20of%20the%20human%20resources%20and%20technology%20ratio%20is%20still%20at%20a%20nascent%20stage.%20China's%20recent%20moves%20are%20a%20wake-up%20call.%20Making%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20fit%20to%20fight%2021st-century%20wars%20should%20be%20the%20topmost%20priority%20for%20any%20government%20that%20takes%20office%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20books%20include%20'India%20and%20the%20Gulf%3A%20Theoretical%20Perspectives%20and%20Policy%20Shifts'%20(Cambridge%20University%20Press)%20and%20'Politics%20and%20Geopolitics%3A%20Decoding%20India's%20Neighbourhood%20Challenge'%20(Rupa)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714643940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-11%2Fxi-jinping_650x400_51510465910.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchina-is-revamping-its-military-and-india-must-not-take-it-lightly-5571658%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20growing%20military%20prowess%20has%20implications%20for%20India's%20defence