-reveals-majority-of-americans-view-tiktok-as-a-tool-of-chinese-influence%2Famp_articleshow%2F109782082.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpoll-reveals-majority-of-americans-view-tiktok-as-a-tool-of-chinese-influence%2Famp_articleshow%2F109782082.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGo%20Hang%20Yourself%26quot%3B%20Not%20Necessarily%20Abetment%20Of%20Suicide%3A%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20High%20Court%20has%20declined%20to%20categorise%20the%20statement%20'go%20hang%20yourself'%20as%20abetment%20of%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20M%20Nagaprasanna%20addressed%20the%20complexity%20of%20determining%20abetment%20of%20suicide%20in%20cases%20involving%20contentious%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20ruling%20stemmed%20from%20a%20petition%20involving%20allegations%20of%20abetment%20of%20suicide%20against%20a%20man%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20death%20of%20a%20priest%20in%20a%20church%20in%20Udupi%20in%20coastal%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20was%20accused%20of%20triggering%20the%20priest's%20suicide%20by%20allegedly%20urging%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20hang%20himself%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20conversation%20about%20the%20priest's%20alleged%20relationship%20with%20the%20petitioner's%20wife.%20The%20defence%20counsel%20argued%20that%20the%20statement%20was%20made%20out%20of%20anguish%20upon%20discovering%20the%20alleged%20affair%2C%20and%20the%20priest's%20decision%20to%20end%20his%20life%20was%20influenced%20by%20the%20affair%20becoming%20known%20to%20others%2C%20rather%20than%20solely%20by%20the%20accused's%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposing%20counsel%20contended%20that%20the%20priest%20took%20his%20own%20life%20due%20to%20the%20accused's%20threatening%20language%20about%20exposing%20the%20affair.%20However%2C%20the%20single%20judge%20bench%2C%20drawing%20on%20precedents%20set%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20emphasised%20that%20such%20statements%20alone%20might%20not%20constitute%20abetment%20to%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20acknowledged%20the%20multifaceted%20reasons%20behind%20the%20priest's%20suicide%2C%20including%20the%20alleged%20illicit%20relationship%20he%20had%20despite%20his%20role%20as%20a%20father%20and%20priest.%20Recognising%20the%20complexities%20of%20human%20psychology%2C%20the%20court%20underscored%20the%20challenge%20of%20deciphering%20the%20human%20mind%20and%20declined%20to%20categorise%20the%20accused's%20statement%20as%20abetment%20to%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20the%20court%20quashed%20the%20case%2C%20emphasising%20the%20intricate%20nature%20of%20human%20behaviour%20and%20the%20inability%20to%20fully%20unravel%20the%20motivations%20behind%20such%20tragic%20incidents.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714641780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fjustice-ge