2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348728%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20soaring%20temperatures%20and%20warnings%20of%20heatwaves%20in%20several%20Indian%20cities%2C%20architects%20share%20how%20to%20build%20homes%20that%20stay%20naturally%20cool%20and%20don't%20require%20air%20conditioning%20at%20all%20times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348728%2Fheatwaves-imd-warning-architect-tips-keep-home-naturally-cool-air-conditioning-summer-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Order%20Organic%20Mangoes%20From%20Farms%20Across%20India%20Using%208%20Online%20Platforms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20remember%20rushing%20home%20from%20school%20to%20savour%20a%20bowl%20filled%20with%20fleshy%2C%20yellow%20squares%20of%20delight%3F%20I%20do.%20Summer%20afternoons%20often%20meant%20eyeing%20the%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ekairi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(raw%20mango)%20trees%2C%20elated%20when%20the%20green%20beauties%20would%20fall%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20be%20almost%20immediately%20scooped%20into%20our%20baskets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20summer%20progresses%2C%20no%20Indian%20is%20a%20stranger%20to%20the%20long%20wait%20that%20ensues%20for%20the%20yellowish-green%20hues%20to%20transform%20into%20its%20ripe%20golden-orange%20form.%20And%20no%20one%20questions%20the%20long%20queues%20outside%20popular%20Gujarati%20joints%20whose%20%3Cem%3Eaamras%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20of%20sweet%20mango%20pulp%20served%20with%20deep-fried%20flatbread)%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20die%20for%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20regulars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20juicy%20fact%20that%20summers%20in%20India%20are%20incomplete%20without%20mango%20dominating%20our%20homes%20and%20palates.%20This%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise.%20Indians%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3