.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVermicompost-kashmir-2-1714386307-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVermicompost-kashmir-2-1714386307-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVermicompost-kashmir-2-1714386307-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVermicompost-kashmir-2-1714386307-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348524%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnnually%2C%20Abdul%20manufactures%2036%2C000%20bags%20of%2050kg%20each.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdul%20manages%20to%20sell%20at%20least%205%20tonnes%20of%20vermicompost%20daily%20to%20local%20farmers%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20With%20his%20efforts%2C%20almost%20the%20entire%20Simthan%20village%20has%20discarded%20chemical%20fertilisers%20to%20use%20organic%20manure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnually%2C%20he%20manufactures%2036%2C000%20bags%20of%2050kg%20each.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20demand%20for%20vermicompost%20in%20entire%20Kashmir.%20With%20the%20current%20production%2C%20I%20am%20catering%20to%20only%2010-15%20villages.%20I%20am%20planning%20to%20boost%20production%20to%201%20lakh%20bags%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20his%20business%20model%2C%20Abdul%20has%20also%20encouraged%20unemployed%20residents%20in%20his%20village%20to%20take%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329041%2Fassam-woman-starts-vermicompost-business-after-husband-death-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evermicompost%20business%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20giving%20free%20training.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20around%2025%20rural%20youth%20and%20150%20women%20homemakers%20trained%20by%20him%20are%20running%20their%20units%20across%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor