re%20is%20no%20vacant%20place%20left%20in%20my%20home%20where%20I%20could%20add%20more%20pots.%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20more%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayanti%2C%20now%2056%20years%20old%2C%20narrates%20that%20it%20was%20during%20her%20childhood%20she%20took%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20gardening.%20Growing%20up%20in%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Odisha%2C%20a%20young%20Jayanti%20lived%20along%20with%20her%20six%20siblings%20and%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20lived%20in%20a%20small%20home.%20My%20father%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278952%2Fkerala-gardener-grows-135-fruit-trees-in-plastic-drums-on-terrace-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20backyard%20and%20we%20helped%20him%20in%20gardening.%20We%20would%20be%20very%20excited%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20the%20well%20and%20water%20all%20the%20plants%20together.%20He%20would%20teach%20us%20how%20to%20take%20care%20of%20plants.%20It%20was%20fun%20to%20be%20in%20the%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20piqued%20her%20interest%20in%20gardening%20and%20her%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20small%20garden%20of%20her%20own.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20would%20not%20grow%20flowering%20plants.%20But%20I%20always%20desired%20to%20grow%20roses%20and%20%3Cem%3Erajanigandha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tuberose).%20So%2C%20when%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20set%20up%20a%20small%20garden%20of%20roses%20and%20other%20flowers.%20My%20father%20would%20bring%20guests%20to%20my%20garden%20and%20proudly%20say%20that%20this%20was%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-4-171336346