Material%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20heatwave%20is%20sweeping%20through%20the%20country%20with%20temperatures%20crossing%2040%20degrees%20Celcius%20in%20many%20cities%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291472%2Fuk-london-europe-heatwave-how-to-stay-cool-traditional-indian-hacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforcing%20us%20to%20use%20air%20conditioners%20at%20all%20times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20the%20climate%20gets%20more%20extreme%2C%20we%20all%20dream%20of%20living%20in%20a%20home%20that%20could%20adapt%20to%20different%20weather%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20way%20homes%20were%20constructed%20earlier%2C%20before%20cement%20became%20a%20necessity%20for%20construction.%20Shipra%20Singhania%20has%20built%20such%20a%20dreamy%20sustainable%20home%20in%20Alwar%2C%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architect%20runs%20Sketch%20Design%20Studio%2C%20and%20built%20this%202%2C000%20square%20feet%20home%20using%20natural%20materials%C2%A0%20and%20revived%20ancient%20techniques.%20The%20home%20is%20built%20using%20mud%20and%20earth%20sacks%20along%20with%20lime%20and%20plaster.%20She%20even%20incorporated%20neem%20leaves%2C%20turmeric%20and%20jaggery%20in%20the%20building%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20edibles%20have%20been%20used%20for%20years%20in%20earthen%20constructions%20due%20to%20their%20many%20properties%20%E2%80%94%20neem%20keeps%20termites%20at%20bay%2C%20while%20jaggery%20is%20a%20great%20binding%20material%2C%20and%20methi%20(fenugreek)%2C%20too%2C%20binds%20the%20bricks%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shipra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20challenge%20was%20designing%20for%20Alwar%E2%80%99s%20extreme%20climate%2C%20with%20temperatures%20going%20from%20as%20high%20as%2041%20degrees%20Celcius%20to%20as%20low%20as%208%20degrees%20Celcius%20in%20the%20winters.%20The%20architect%20designed%20the%20home%20in%20a%20strategic%20mann